      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1173689935,
      "version": 523,
      "versionNonce": 1666645423,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772865759582,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Waster of time. Instead tell the interviewer that \nI am gonna calculate the estimation\nduring the high level design if I need to take \nany decision from the estimation.",
      "fontSize": 20,
